title: WESTinnoMAR
objective: The proposed project addresses the action for ìEstablishing services ìEnhancing the innovation management capacity of SMEsî in the Enterprise Europe Networkî to improve the innovation management capacity of SMEs. The activities foreseen under this proposal is to give Activity 4 of EEN services to SMEs. 10 full enhancing SMEsí innovation management capacity service packages will be offered to SMEís till the end of 2018 and every service package is foreseen as 7 days in the proposal. Additionally, 14 day KAM serviceswill be offered for successful beneficiaries of SME instrument Phase 1.
